title: LF Ranked team [Diamond V top/mid/adc]
body:
Looking for a ranked 5s team to play with, wanting a somewhat serious team that uses voice communication(skype/teamspeak, etc..).
I have most of my experince in top/mid/adc and a bit in support, willing to learn to fit a role in a team.
IGN: NWA Ice Cube
Age: 18
I'm usually looking to play later on in the day and on the weekends, msg me if you want to know more.
